==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tonguester
<hw>Tongue"ster</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who uses his
tongue; a talker; a story-teller; a gossip.</def>
<mark>[Poetic.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Step by step we rose to greatness; through the
<qex>tonguesters</qex> we may fall.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tongue-tie</ent>⟦br⟧
